Package com.webfirmframework.wffweb.tag.html.attribute

Class Rev

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.tag.core.AbstractTagBase
      • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.tag.html.attribute.core.AbstractAttribute
        • com.webfirmframework.wffweb.tag.html.attribute.Rev
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TagBase, AAttributable, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    public class Rev
extends AbstractAttribute
implements AAttributable
    This attribute specifies a reverse link, the inverse relationship of the rel attribute. It is useful for indicating where an object came from, such as the author of a document. rev attribute for the element. NB: This attribute is not supported by html5.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
